5. Write a Ruby script to find the greatest of three numbers

print "Enter the value of x:"
x = gets.to_i
print "Enter the value of y:"
y = gets.to_i
print "Enter the value of z:"
z = gets.to_i
if x >= y and x >= z
  puts "x = #{x} is the greatest no."
elsif y >= x and y >= z
  puts "y = #{y} is the greatest no."
else 
  puts "z = #{z} is the greatest no."
end
